          <div class = "section-b"> 
            <div class = "row">
              <div class = "col-md-8 col-md-offset-2" >
                <h3><i class="fa fa-paperclip"></i> Materials Needed:</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>A laptop with internet access</li>
                  <li>A modern web browser (Chrome is recommended) with cookies enabled</li>
