          <div class = "section-a"> 
            <div class = "row">
              <div class = "col-md-8 col-md-offset-2" >
                <h3>Game Board Functionality:</h3>
                <p>	XXX A. Reveal/conceal answers
		- Click in the specific answer field to reveal/conceal it.
	B. Operate strike (red 'X') counter
		- Simply click the red X's on the bottom of the game board. 
		- Clicking after all three X's are red will automatically switch 								control of the round to the other team.
	C. Switch teams depending on whose turn it is
		- Either use the three-strikes method described above, or click on the 						appropriate team box in lower left/right corner (notice the orange box that 						denotes which team is highlighted).
	D. Appropriately allocate points at the end of a round
		1 - Highlight which team is to be awarded with the rounds points (click the 						appropriate team box in lower left/right corner).
		2 - Only have answers correctly guessed by the winning team revealed and all 					other answers concealed (click in the specific answer field to reveal/conceal it).
		3 - Click “Award points and continue”  to award points. The number of revealed
		 answers will be equal to the number of points allocated to the highlighted/winning team.
	E. Jump to any question
		- Click link in lower left corner “Question _of 6” and navigate to appropriate question.</p>
      </div> <!--col 6 -->
